result.calculatedFormula:
IF(
  ISPICKVAL(npe01__Primary_Address_Type__c,"Home"),
  IF(ISBLANK(MailingStreet), "", MailingStreet & ", ") & 
  IF(ISBLANK(MailingCity), "", MailingCity & ", ")& 
  IF(ISBLANK(MailingState), "", MailingState & " ")& 
  IF(ISBLANK(MailingPostalCode), "", MailingPostalCode) & 
  IF(ISBLANK(MailingCountry), "", ", " &MailingCountry)
,
IF(ISPICKVAL(npe01__Secondary_Address_Type__c,"Home"),
  IF(ISBLANK(OtherStreet), "", OtherStreet & ", ") & 
  IF(ISBLANK(OtherCity), "", OtherCity & ", ")& 
  IF(ISBLANK(OtherState), "", OtherState & " ")& 
  IF(ISBLANK(OtherPostalCode), "", OtherPostalCode) & 
  IF(ISBLANK(OtherCountry), "", ", " & OtherCountry)
  ,""
)
)
result.inlineHelpText: Formula: Uses primary address type field to determine Home Address from Mailing or Other address.
result.label: Home Address
result.name: npe01__Home_Address__c

result.inlineHelpText: Formula: In order of preference, the SYSTEM_AccountType field, the Account Type field, and "Organization".
